sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant CDN as CDN Edge
    participant API as Suggest API
    participant Shard as Trie Shard
    participant Build as Build Pipeline
    participant Snap as Snapshot Store

    Note over Build,Snap: OFFLINE BUILD (hourly)
    Build->>Build: aggregate query freqs from logs
    Build->>Build: build trie bottom-up, cache top-K per node
    Build->>Snap: write trie snapshot
    Snap-)Shard: push + atomic swap

    Note over C,Shard: ONLINE SERVE (per keystroke)
    C->>CDN: GET /suggest?q=goo
    alt popular prefix cached
        CDN-->>C: top-K suggestions
    else miss
        CDN->>API: forward request
        API->>API: route by prefix to shard
        API->>Shard: walk to node "goo"
        Shard-->>API: cached top-K (no subtree scan)
        API-->>CDN: top-K + cache
        CDN-->>C: suggestions
    end
